  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "It has been reported that group chats performance starts degrading when the number of users > 50 ( it might happen earlier).\r\n\r\nThis results in dropped messages and delayed communication.\r\n\r\nThat's likely a limit with pairwise encryption, we were aware that performance wise it does not scale, and eventually it would need to be improved to support large groups.",
